---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900">About Falcon Speech</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">Transforming lives through innovative virtual speech therapy</p>
    </div>

    <div class="prose prose-lg mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          At Falcon Speech, we're dedicated to making professional speech therapy accessible to everyone through innovative virtual solutions. Our mission is to break down geographical barriers and provide high-quality speech therapy services to clients in their homes, offices, or wherever they feel most comfortable.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Why Choose Virtual Speech Therapy?</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-4 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-2 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span>Convenience: Access professional therapy from the comfort of your home</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-2 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span>Flexibility: Schedule sessions that fit your busy lifestyle</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary mr-2 mt-1 flex-shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span>Consistency: Maintain regular therapy sessions without travel barriers</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-8">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Team</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
          Our team consists of licensed speech-language pathologists with extensive experience in virtual therapy. Each therapist is certified by the American Speech-Language-Hearing Association (ASHA) and maintains the highest standards of professional practice.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Our Commitment</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600">
          We're committed to providing personalized, evidence-based therapy services that meet each client's unique needs. Through continuous professional development and the use of cutting-edge technology, we ensure the highest quality of care in the virtual setting.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>